# Cloud Security Best Practices Applied

### Principle of Least Privilege

Only required access granted.

### Secure Administrative Access

SSH restricted to trusted source.

### Network-Level Security

Firewall controls enforced before reaching the host.

### Attack Surface Reduction

No unnecessary ports exposed.

### Resource Isolation

Network tags used to isolate policy application.

### Temporary Lab Infrastructure

Resources removed after testing.

