# Conclusion

This project successfully demonstrated the implementation of secure remote administrative access in Google Cloud Platform through the use of VPC Firewall Rules and network segmentation.

By restricting SSH access to a trusted public IP address and applying targeted firewall policies using network tags, the environment adhered to industry-recommended cloud security practices.

The lab provided practical experience with cloud infrastructure security, network access control, and secure cloud operations, aligning closely with the responsibilities of an entry-level Cloud Security Engineer.
